{
  "stem": "25773.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the day she kept her behind the cupboard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She probably was shot dead afterwards by Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my uncle who was my auntie's husband, came home a day before and saw that his wife was not there, so he give himself up to the Germans immediately.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I slept overnight there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My brother was deposited to this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I took him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I had to leave my aunt-- another aunt of mine came in the evening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she brought-- she worked in one of the shops still, so she brought some little food, some, I don't know, kind of vegetables.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She made again a little soup with some bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we all ate it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I slept overnight and wept all the time nonstop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then left my-- said goodbye to my beloved grandmother and to this aunt and went back to my small ghetto, where I still had my father and my stepmother.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that I was not taken by crossing the no man's land and taken by the Germans was just an accident.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the selections.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About my personal selection, I'll tell you later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the selections, there usually came a few armored cars with armed soldiers, rifles with the foreboding-looking uniform, Prussian, and with the green uniforms, and the big boots, and the officers with the leather coats, fabulously dressed.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sometimes they had a dog with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And young people, very young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came to every house and shouted, 'rous!' 'Rous!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rous!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Rous!' Means come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Jewish policemen had to help them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Jewish policemen, they went up and down and searched in the-- you know, being too ardent in wanting to help.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were forced also to help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and, and so the people took little bundles.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
